": "AOTVR_FullRelease_Store_Screenshot_01.png", "id": "900115875571190", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982725_900115882237856_5872210500042138395_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ULiNkzbTZYcQ7kNvgGfhlgW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAqgZ_VlkZgUOigTrRMe_yijE9NwbW4FFqvtCAJO2QkUQ&oe=676809F2"}, {"file_name": "AOTVR_FullRelease_Store_Screenshot_02.png", "id": "799141252339429", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031509_799141255672762_2662005463467922782_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MhdZvp4mOgcQ7kNvgGwnbx-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZqkoeKFAMn-BdgdAQbmDfdGphZRIhuSaim5Gg_2VH1Q&oe=67681538"}, {"file_name": "AOTVR_FullRelease_Store_Screenshot_03.png", "id": "975722784600850", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75392232_975722787934183_8955032621721619664_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dWESIHyPeMAQ7kNvgFtwKR9&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOyB_h6k5Pgg3IVNOl3I2PSYiYAAFYiq2ZoRwWmF9_9w&oe=67681026"}, {"file_name": "AOTVR_FullRelease_Store_Screenshot_04.png", "id": "600354029006136", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035327_600354032339469_8658180179906125260_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=d7RJgEk6MM8Q7kNvgHt8NIU&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZBiZQYFkzYvAwD9fCGRcfEXnFgfwUaeyrVI2RJEYJ8g&oe=6767FFD7"}, {"file_name": "AOTVR_FullRelease_Store_Screenshot_05.png", "id": "2414997175497957", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575352_2414997178831290_8097939323630436233_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hklYH5Bf_ScQ7kNvgEjJmxy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAMW7-kBlceTztbXBSo7nTEkejmn4LF8niNGklW-zvQdA&oe=676813C6"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "FREEDOM_2560x1440_CompleteEditionAvailable_EN.png", "id": "523206467537011", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/468752496_523206470870344_633342755118363834_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=S51KzZ6pKyoQ7kNvgHv67by&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCazJ6vmnj2pJ8AL-KXcRBdxuqOssZCzHauNdeIelUFTg&oe=6767E263"}, "display_name": "Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable - Part.1", "keywords": ["AttackonTitan", "AoT", "Shingeki", "Action", "Hunting"], "long_description": "---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n{1742353936601045}\n{2026049414581724}\n# Complete Edition (Part.1 + 2) Available Now!\n\nPrepare for combat with Omni-Directional Mobility Gear and fly head-first into battle! Defy all odds and eliminate the Titans!\n\nAttack on Titan VR: Unbreakable, the first-person action-adventure VR platformer based on the highly acclaimed manga \u201cAttack on Titan\u201d and the latest installment of the VR series. \n\n{1280368342833344}\n\n\nJoin the Scout Regiment as an aspiring recruit and help defend mankind from the Titan invasion.\n\n\n# Omni-Directional Mobility Gear\nUtilize the Omni-Directional Mobility Gear to maneuver through the air and combat the onslaught of Titans! \n{1195760871453526}\n\n\n# The Titan Threat\nTitans rely on their instincts to hunt humans and satisfy their insatiable appetites.\nOvercome the fear of death and lay waste to the Titan army!\n{1042373100565202}\n\n\n# Distinct Weapons\nEach weapon offers unique characteristics that can alter the course of battle and how it is approached!\n{469443659357575}\n\n\n\n**Additionally, the Thunder Spear Unlock Event is on the horizon. Join forces with Scouts from around the world and prepare to take on this global challenge.**\n\n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd. \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.\n", "short_description": "Complete Edition (Part.1 + 2) Available Now!\nFight for your life against man-eating Titans in Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable. In a thrilling mix of hunting and action, join the Scout Regiment and put on your Omni-Directional Mobility Gear to defend and protect humanity against the Titans. \n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd.   \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc."}]}, "developer_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://univrs.jp/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://univrs.jp/terms-of-use/", "publisher_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://aotvrub.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1008279844328894"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "FLYING"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "27742631065352590"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982699_881170787505756_8279773858403794462_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QlQCkKxpOpwQ7kNvgFwlLzQ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDOGVpgAQOuF0nq-tJ8o-adrzBAKk3ERry8NrUQZnh3oA&oe=6767F060"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable - Part.1", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "A